{
  "texts": [
    "This scale consists of 16 items and is rated using the Likert 5-point scale (1 = almost never, 5 = almost always).",
    "The higher the score, the greater the difficulty in regulating emotions.",
    "Previous research has demonstrated the suitability and good reliability and validity of this scale for the middle school student population [34].",
    "The Cronbach's alpha coefficient for the scale in this study was 0.94.",
    "ProcedurePrior to the initiation of the study, informed consent forms were required to be signed by all participants and their guardians."
  ]
}